窄 0.1 个百分点；二手住宅环比下降 0.5%，降幅比上月扩大 0.1 个百分点。 从同比看，9 月份，二线城市新建商品住宅销售价格同比上涨 0.2%，涨幅比上月回落 0.1 个百分点；二手住宅同比下降 3.2%，降幅比上月扩大 0.2 个百分点。三线城市新建商品住宅和二手住宅销售价格同比分别下降 1.4% 和 3.5%，降幅均与上月相同。 9 月份，70 个大中城市中，新建商品住宅销售价格同比下降城市有 45 个，比上月增加 1 个，较年内高点减少 10 个；二手住宅销售价格同比下降城市有 67 个，比上月增加 1 个。9 月份一线城市商品住宅销售价格环比稳中微涨 _ 地产界 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626793520"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5J+R0q+FwYRqEAMaCTEwMTU2NjU4NiDjlcKpBjAAOFZAKHIJNjI2NzkzNTIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1697774966.178768", "card_id": "Q_626892841", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 163}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "S13 瑞士轮首轮焦点战 BLG 1:0 力克 KT，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1c78765a64bccbe5a36d19dc1126122e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626892841"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI5J+R0q+FwYRqEAMaCTEwMTU4ODYwOCD8wMSpBjAAONABQClyCTYyNjg5Mjg0MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1697774966.179817", "card_id": "Q_626878598", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 86}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "S13 入围赛首轮 WBG 1:0 NRG 取得开门红，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3c5b86c8a309a703543ca9c39da2179f_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626878598"}